column5: How much is gas prices these days in Dryden or Sioux Lookout?
Was just up there last weekend. $1.09 per litre Canadian at the stations, over $1.35 per litre Canadian at the resort. Scott
Wish I were up there right now to buy some of that gasoline.
don,t worry we will save you as much as you want. just let me know as we have a gas station and can put some away for you.

teddi, I always fill up in Ear Falls on the way to Red Lake. Takes my van back to International Falls for the next gas purchase. May 14, I was about 10 minutes north of Ear Falls when I got a close photo of a wolf, two bears and a moose, all within 12 minutes. Saw lots more moose and many more bears than usual, both going and coming. Bears were sluggish May 14. Maybe they knew what was coming the next morning.Met your neighbor, Don Maw, May 30 on the way home. Shook his hand, but didn't get a photo of him.
